{"id": "ChIJpV9scwC_woARVhaBXDL6sX4", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 165, "displayName": {"text": "Kanomwaan Thai Gelato and Dessert Cafe", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJpV9scwC_woARVhaBXDL6sX4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWWVluWkJaRE5zU1VkdVdXNDVWVnBYVm04d1EzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "DO NOT SLEEP ON THIS!\n\nOrdered the Mango Sticky Rice Shaved Ice … and wowwwww! It did not disappoint. Since they ran out of mango ice cream, we ate it with pandan ice cream instead and again, WOW - this was a great alternative!\n\nI was expecting an overly sweet shaved ice dessert, but was met with a perfect balance of shaved ice, with mangoes, pandan ice cream, sticky rice, mango puree, and sweet milk. There are hidden little mango pieces on the bottom of the shaved ice.\n\nDefinitely large enough to share between three people, or two hungry people. Or better yet - large enough to treat yourself!\n\nEven after a full dinner, I grew an extra stomach to finish this dessert. I cannot stop dreaming about this. Please try! Highly recommend. 🧡", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "DO NOT SLEEP ON THIS!\n\nOrdered the Mango Sticky Rice Shaved Ice … and wowwwww! It did not disappoint. Since they ran out of mango ice cream, we ate it with pandan ice cream instead and again, WOW - this was a great alternative!\n\nI was expecting an overly sweet shaved ice dessert, but was met with a perfect balance of shaved ice, with mangoes, pandan ice cream, sticky rice, mango puree, and sweet milk. There are hidden little mango pieces on the bottom of the shaved ice.\n\nDefinitely large enough to share between three people, or two hungry people. Or better yet - large enough to treat yourself!\n\nEven after a full dinner, I grew an extra stomach to finish this dessert. I cannot stop dreaming about this. Please try! Highly recommend. 🧡", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Monique Obiniana", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112082285945892425970/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXFNiMl4QotfwA7DTDgWwtjEq2mhQjFskurxJBiCQgIK1BZVfF=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-21T02:25:01.045322548Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWWVluWkJaRE5zU1VkdVdXNDVWVnBYVm04d1EzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWWVluWkJaRE5zU1VkdVdXNDVWVnBYVm04d1EzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf00736c5fa5:0x7eb1fa325c811656"}, {"name": "places/ChIJpV9scwC_woARVhaBXDL6sX4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wb1VXUTNXSEkxYTAxblNWUTRiM0JDVFZKdWNsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "A fun spin on classic thai dessert flavors! LOVE the mango sticky rice shaved ice and pandan toast!!!!  A successful nod to the classic flavors of mango sticky rice and the shaved ice stays fluffy.  Actual mango and sticky rice is also served with coconut and mango sauces that accompany the shaved as perfectly.  Servings are huge and it helps to grab the water cups to make your own parfait like concoction to share the desserts with your group.  There are also a handful of unique gelato flavors and drinks to try as well.  Space is limited inside and it can be get busy, but it does help that they manage the seating to only be allowed after you have ordered and they look around to see if there are tables for you.  Service can be better.  The handful of times I have visited, the workers are either preoccupied or somewhat rushing you.  Parking in the lot is valet only unless you find some metered spots on the street or free residential parking within the area.  Overall, a delicious dessert destination!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "A fun spin on classic thai dessert flavors! LOVE the mango sticky rice shaved ice and pandan toast!!!!  A successful nod to the classic flavors of mango sticky rice and the shaved ice stays fluffy.  Actual mango and sticky rice is also served with coconut and mango sauces that accompany the shaved as perfectly.  Servings are huge and it helps to grab the water cups to make your own parfait like concoction to share the desserts with your group.  There are also a handful of unique gelato flavors and drinks to try as well.  Space is limited inside and it can be get busy, but it does help that they manage the seating to only be allowed after you have ordered and they look around to see if there are tables for you.  Service can be better.  The handful of times I have visited, the workers are either preoccupied or somewhat rushing you.  Parking in the lot is valet only unless you find some metered spots on the street or free residential parking within the area.  Overall, a delicious dessert destination!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amanda Potchanatayparuk", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102629987364925365749/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjqDbKM0QcGIWR_oCvu_KKVxtnqVVS_AVFH1chLldi-EEH4Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-11T03:13:16.258054302Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wb1VXUTNXSEkxYTAxblNWUTRiM0JDVFZKdWNsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wb1VXUTNXSEkxYTAxblNWUTRiM0JDVFZKdWNsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf00736c5fa5:0x7eb1fa325c811656"}, {"name": "places/ChIJpV9scwC_woARVhaBXDL6sX4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wd05GTm9OM0E1Vm10M01IcDBNbEowVUdaS1MyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "They have the most fluffy and light milk-based shaved ice that wasn’t too sweet, similar to 綿綿冰! This is the kind of dessert where the texture can’t fully be communicated until you actually consume it yourself.\n\nI would recommend trying it first without the evaporated milk to really savor the flavors of the ice itself. It looks huge but it’s light enough that a party of 4 can fairly easily clear it, whereas a single or double scoop gelato would be perfect for 2 people.\n\nThe shaved ice itself comes with a gelato scoop on top that was heavenly smooth and creamy, so you can effectively try both. This place clears Oakobing and Wanderlust, respectively, easily.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "They have the most fluffy and light milk-based shaved ice that wasn’t too sweet, similar to 綿綿冰! This is the kind of dessert where the texture can’t fully be communicated until you actually consume it yourself.\n\nI would recommend trying it first without the evaporated milk to really savor the flavors of the ice itself. It looks huge but it’s light enough that a party of 4 can fairly easily clear it, whereas a single or double scoop gelato would be perfect for 2 people.\n\nThe shaved ice itself comes with a gelato scoop on top that was heavenly smooth and creamy, so you can effectively try both. This place clears Oakobing and Wanderlust, respectively, easily.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anna", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108989905571960919053/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDfJK7w1fmx_Jh1hFg8FS9KuGK4aPUfuyOQ1BU3RzqrmAzH5Y=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-20T18:48:05.087643632Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wd05GTm9OM0E1Vm10M01IcDBNbEowVUdaS1MyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wd05GTm9OM0E1Vm10M01IcDBNbEowVUdaS1MyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf00736c5fa5:0x7eb1fa325c811656"}, {"name": "places/ChIJpV9scwC_woARVhaBXDL6sX4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kaVUycGlhbWhuWVdaNlNraFpZMlJZUzIxdGRtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I recommend the coconut milk butterfly pea.\nThe blue color looks fresh and beautiful.\n\nIt tastes really good.\nThe coconut flavor is light but noticeable, and the ice cream itself is very rich.\n\nIt was a good dessert option.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I recommend the coconut milk butterfly pea.\nThe blue color looks fresh and beautiful.\n\nIt tastes really good.\nThe coconut flavor is light but noticeable, and the ice cream itself is very rich.\n\nIt was a good dessert option.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "AJ", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106675166890962112351/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtIi-cOuSHsCiIRiR9BjKnsvEeYdoA7D6byFlAXCqhWqD4lp4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-25T06:55:53.264154599Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kaVUycGlhbWhuWVdaNlNraFpZMlJZUzIxdGRtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kaVUycGlhbWhuWVdaNlNraFpZMlJZUzIxdGRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf00736c5fa5:0x7eb1fa325c811656"}, {"name": "places/ChIJpV9scwC_woARVhaBXDL6sX4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGcmJsaFNRemhyZUZNemVXOVVUelUwVEhGa2JGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I recommend this Thai gelato place.\nThis cute little shop has quite unusual gelato flavors, Thai inspired.  Delicious. Great drinks also.  Staff were very friendly.\nParking a little challenging as the options are limited street parking or a paid strip mall parking lot with no validation offered. Best to walk here if possible.\nThis is a place worth visiting for tasty treats.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I recommend this Thai gelato place.\nThis cute little shop has quite unusual gelato flavors, Thai inspired.  Delicious. Great drinks also.  Staff were very friendly.\nParking a little challenging as the options are limited street parking or a paid strip mall parking lot with no validation offered. Best to walk here if possible.\nThis is a place worth visiting for tasty treats.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "T McMinn", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103710072584870041219/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUD-PMbKSqdWu0tCpErd_Xw9DhlpgVVkIGvf6tyyDthoAh1nrb7BQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-04T15:43:30.759865725Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGcmJsaFNRemhyZUZNemVXOVVUelUwVEhGa2JGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGcmJsaFNRemhyZUZNemVXOVVUelUwVEhGa2JGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf00736c5fa5:0x7eb1fa325c811656"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJpV9scwC_woARVhaBXDL6sX4/photos/AWCwydjFO4ocwH-S7gTyD_xzoRPDEjWgPnhqNWDz4YzU71CsIZcZ6JnqMLPIiocXvLEO8yrVwOtHei0WFgC6t7_Ns3AjaX5W0aR9BhbjNISZJ-WJbwRo4K2dbLbq4JgvI_s06BeRsPvUG_Sput8GUVSdwMXtOrIXolFh1y-l2yvfN5GS45YIacYN5cY9wNBSsDUyTFVvCO2xLHMgZywxGBqX6ywezhcZOfwsYJZxC91jx7IKvE-7ZVaYvaNJp2XoI4agDYNGEOH4Uyrqa5aFu_-CkCZS4fRf_LBkJIHYNZMMoyhbUnLgwRrzge_DKaUgy4oNWW9PNgpcZn98fPjjCcINO0Zr1OSKg9tCRc-Fb0-zfnqa2KZVTo5VNAbqoNNBhrV6SoSZDmxL2v6lbHy_nV1Ibq9E3dSatdvByNLKMxIZ2Ib8ozL1uDT1iCmXqsNBMg", "widthPx": 4032, "heightPx": 3024, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "T McMinn", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/103710072584870041219", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUD-PMbKSqdWu0tCpErd_Xw9DhlpgVVkIGvf6tyyDthoAh1nrb7BQ=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhBE9rr_ch3x5in10eSLlGvX&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_